Title: Outlook Weekend: My New Mum
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cstzb2
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 14 Aug 2017
Raised as a child of the Black Panther party, Mary Williams became the unlikely daughter of celebrity, Jane Fonda. Sharon Shattuck's understanding of what a normal family was changed on Christmas day when she discovered photos of her father dressed as a woman. Sharon's dad explained to her that he felt more comfortable as a member of the opposite sex. Image: Family Paper Chain Credit: mattjeacock/Getty Images Show less